          "reviewTitle": "my every day makeup",
          "reviewText": "I absolutely love this cushion. I was looking for a replacement for my CU Skin since the shade I need is hard to find here and has to be ordered from Korea. Everything about this cushion is great. It gives a balanced glow \u2014 not too shiny. If you don\u2019t like looking glowy in the sun, you can always set your T-zone with a translucent powder, but I personally love the finish as it is. It has light to medium coverage, which I prefer. If I have any breakouts, I\u2019d rather spot-conceal them than wear heavy, full coverage that makes my skin look like drywall texture. It also works beautifully with the Clio primer from the same brand. Highly recommend.",
          "reviewDate": "Reviewed in the United States on March 1, 2026",
