        {
          "reviewTitle": "Amazing formulation, but now missing sunscreen",
          "reviewText": "I love this formulation--it's low coverage, but buildable, and very very dewy and skin-like. Perfect for a no makeup look. If you find it oily or greasy, I recommend giving it a minute or two to dry down before continuing the rest of your makeup. One unfortunate con (but this isn't specific to this product, so I'm not docking my rating) is that this version does NOT contain SPF. I've previously purchased this product in Korea and it always had SPF, so I'm assuming this may be a result of the new US regulations governing foreign sunscreens.",
